TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select c.division_id, c.customer_account_code, c.customer_group_code, cg.group_desc, c.parent_account, c.account_name, c.soldto, c.xrf_account, c.customer_sequence_num, c.userid, c.customer_rank, cs.seg_desc, cc.channel_desc, ccg.channel_group_desc, cz.zone_desc, s1.name as s1_name, s2.name as s2_name, s3.name as s3_name, co.country_desc, c.chain_account_desc, co.Country_Code, c.customer_Event_Group_Id, ceg.Customer_Event_Group from edm.dbo.customer c, edm.dbo.customer_group cg, edm.dbo.customer_seg cs, edm.dbo.customer_channel cc, edm.dbo.customer_channel_group ccg, edm.dbo.customer_zone cz, edm.dbo.customer_sales_resp_name1 s1, edm.dbo.customer_sales_resp_name2 s2, edm.dbo.customer_sales_resp_name3 s3, edm.dbo.country co, edm.dbo.[CUSTOMER_EVENT_GROUP ] ceg where c.division_id = 'GF' and c.customer_group_code = cg.group_code and c.seg_id = cs.seg_id and c.channel_id = cc.channel_id and c.channel_group_id = ccg.channel_group_id and c.zone_id = cz.zone_id and c.sales_resp_name1_id = s1.name_id and c.sales_resp_name2_id = s2.name_id and c.sales_resp_name3_id = s3.name_id and c.country_id = co.country_id and c.customer_Event_Group_Id = ceg.Customer_Event_Group_ID and c.update_date >= GETDATE()-2
